                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370227-903-offence-1 t18370227-cd-167"></join>4th of February</rs>, 1 half-crown, the monies of <persName id="t18370227-name-1357" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370227-name-1357" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
